data.title: The Exorcist 50th Anniversary Event
data.meta_description:
Fans gathered at the Palm Springs Cultural Center for a screening of what is arguably the scariest motion picture ever made. NBC Palm Springs Steve Sumrall was there, as well as an actress named Eileen Dietz. (You may not have heard of her, but her contribution to this Hollywood classic is undeniable).
This story was written and reported by Steve Sumrall.
